    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Class Zero Seven is a third person brawler that tells the story of a wide nation fight against substance abuse. Play as Rin, a newly transferred student with a mysterious background among her peers. Stand off against the Rivalry Gangs and the looming threat of a Criminal Organization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BE THE DELINQUENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The gangs are looking for victims. You're in for a fight and they know what's coming to them. Topple the reign of Gangs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752990/extras/5e9af56437548fb381666f19ec9e0f33.poster.avif?t=1749020864\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752990/extras/5e9af56437548fb381666f19ec9e0f33.webm?t=1749020864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752990/extras/5e9af56437548fb381666f19ec9e0f33.mp4?t=1749020864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THIS IS YOUR PLAYGROUND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Schools and the Streets are filled with Toys for you to play with. You decide how to win the fights!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752990/extras/83eaf70ac2b53f477972b8e98221c85b.poster.avif?t=1749020864\" width=640 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752990/extras/83eaf70ac2b53f477972b8e98221c85b.webm?t=1749020864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752990/extras/83eaf70ac2b53f477972b8e98221c85b.mp4?t=1749020864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A VIBRANT TOWN WITH STORIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features multiple traversable maps. From visiting different schools to interesting places in the town. Perfect for bonding with your Allies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752990/extras/0c3ac6fd48c510c07e6a50cd1fd9f825.poster.avif?t=1749020864\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752990/extras/0c3ac6fd48c510c07e6a50cd1fd9f825.webm?t=1749020864\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752990/extras/0c3ac6fd48c510c07e6a50cd1fd9f825.mp4?t=1749020864\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Refreshing take on Third Person Brawler.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters with lovable quirks.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Strong Narrative.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Playable Characters each with Unique Gameplay Elements.</p></li></ul>",
